---
title: Quick Teriyaki Pork Noodle Stir-Fry with Veggies & Crushed Peanuts
description: Sure, we've been accused of being a little nutty. So what? When the results are as quick and delicious as these warm pork noodles with plenty of tasty crunch from the crushed peanuts, we'll wear the nutty badge with pride!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/657a461da65f6d71569fbf08-37f059c0.jpeg
